TASK2
Write a program to find sum of digits a two digit number(23)

program:

class SumOfDigits{
  public static void main(String args[]){
        int number=23;
        int tensDigit = number / 10;
        int onesDigit = number % 10;
        int sum = tensDigit + onesDigit;
        System.out.println(sum);
}
}
Ans: 5
